### Int64Range

 
Specifies the int64 start and end of the range using half-open interval semantics [start,
end).

```yaml
"start": int
"end": int

```

| Field | Type | Description | Default |
| ----- | ---- | ----------- |----------- | 
| `start` | `int` | start of the range (inclusive). |  |
| `end` | `int` | end of the range (exclusive). |  |
